    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>African tree cultivated as a source of oil in West and Central Africa, where it originated, and in Malaysia and Indonesia, and as an ornamental tree in many subtropical areas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
